&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Commercial Lines Account Coordinator is responsible for daily servicing of clients including new and renewal business processing while maintaining exceptional customer relations with clients. This includes regularly interacting with new and existing clients as needed. The Account Coordinator is also responsible for devising creative solutions to meet client needs as to insurance coverage. This position reviews processed policies as needed, services clients in a timely manner, and performs such other duties as are required to establish, service and maintain accounts.&lt;/p&gt;
