&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://foundationrp.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foundation Risk Partners&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;, one of the fastest growing insurance brokerage and consulting firms in the US, is adding an experienced&lt;em&gt; Commercial Lines Account Manager&lt;/em&gt; to their&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://acentria.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Acentria&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt; team.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Commercial Lines Account Manager leads the team closely in conjunction with the Producer in developing strategy for retention of renewals and new business acquisition. This position regularly exercises discretion and independent judgement on accounts including product and pricing determinations, affecting, interpreting and implementing various company policies. The Account Manager interacts and provides professional support to clients and team members. The Account Manager initiates renewal process including preparing submission to proposing and binding coverages as needed. This position also performs all other duties required to establish, service, and maintain accounts.&lt;/p&gt;
